To avoid accidental use of raw pointers, radar::find_max_peak_c&apos;s constructor is in a private implementation class. radar::find_max_peak_c::make is the public interface for creating new instances.

Args:
    samp_rate : 
    threshold : 
    samp_protect : 
    max_freq : 
